real-estate.title: Entire loft hosted by Trinidad
real-estate.desc: Apartment located 6 minutes walk from the metro station Hospital de Móstoles and the hospital itself. 3 minutes from the Coronel de Palma medical center. Very close to the Mercadona and the Plaza. Very well connected by road and means of transport (metro and bus). It is located in a quiet area. The very cozy house with lots of light and very independent. Very easy to access the house, since it is at street level. Includes appliances such as microwave, mini stereo, refrigerator, oven, vitro.
